    • Enum Constant Detail

      • SHUFFLE_MEMBER_LIST

        public static final ClientProperty SHUFFLE_MEMBER_LIST
        Client shuffles the given member list to prevent all clients to connect to the same node when this property is set to false. When it is set to true, the client tries to connect to the nodes in the given order.

      • HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT

        public static final ClientProperty HEARTBEAT_TIMEOUT
        Client sends heartbeat messages to the members and this is the timeout for this sending operations. If there is not any message passing between the client and member within the given time via this property in milliseconds, the connection will be closed.

      • HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL

        public static final ClientProperty HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL
        Time interval between the heartbeats sent by the client to the nodes.

      • EVENT_THREAD_COUNT

        public static final ClientProperty EVENT_THREAD_COUNT
        Number of the threads to handle the incoming event packets.

      • EVENT_QUEUE_CAPACITY

        public static final ClientProperty EVENT_QUEUE_CAPACITY
        Capacity of the executor that handles the incoming event packets.

      • INVOCATION_TIMEOUT_SECONDS

        public static final ClientProperty INVOCATION_TIMEOUT_SECONDS
        Time to give up on invocation when a member in the member list is not reachable.

      • MAX_CONCURRENT_INVOCATIONS

        public static final ClientProperty MAX_CONCURRENT_INVOCATIONS
        The maximum number of concurrent invocations allowed.

        To prevent the system from overloading, user can apply a constraint on the number of concurrent invocations. If the maximum number of concurrent invocations has been exceeded and a new invocation comes in, then hazelcast will throw HazelcastOverloadException

        By default it is configured as Integer.MaxValue.

      • DISCOVERY_SPI_ENABLED

        public static final ClientProperty DISCOVERY_SPI_ENABLED

        Enables the Discovery SPI lookup over the old native implementations. This property is temporary and will eventually be removed when the experimental marker is removed.

        Discovery SPI is disabled by default

      • INTERNAL_EXECUTOR_POOL_SIZE

        public static final ClientProperty INTERNAL_EXECUTOR_POOL_SIZE
        Configures pool size of internal client executor. Private configuration, for internal usage only.
